    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CactusBandido - Multiplayer Chaos in the Wild West 🌵</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An online party game where up to 6 players incarnate outlaw cacti competing for treasure. Fight in real-time, steal gold, and fill your cart before the sheriff catches you. The atmosphere is wacky, the rules simple, the chaos guaranteed.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GOLD RUSH - The Main Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match lasts <strong>10 minutes</strong> and follows the same fierce objective: <strong>become the richest.</strong> Here's how:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏃 <strong>Race</strong> to the bank while dodging the sheriff and his spotlights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 <strong>Steal</strong> as much gold from the bank as possible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Fight</strong> other cacti with punches and power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🐎 Secure</strong> your loot in your cart</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Win</strong> if you have the most gold at the end</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But beware: chaotic events can turn everything upside down at any time!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Game Elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Cactus-Steam_Plan_de_travail_1_copie_4.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Render-avec-fon.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat - </strong>Intense showdowns against other cacti. Every blow counts to loot or protect your treasure. No subtlety, just raw brawl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Cactus-Steam_Plan_de_travail_1_copie_3.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/BONUS-plusnom.jpg?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power-ups - </strong>Discover powerful bonuses: <u>offensive</u> (attack others), <u>defensive</u> (protect yourself), <u>passive</u> (boost your earnings). Transform your battles and strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Cactus-Steam_Plan_de_travail_1.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Rendu-Blender-Train+pouletos-trans.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Events - </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sheriff's Rage:</strong> Spotlights strengthen, the bank becomes more dangerous</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Express Train:</strong> Crushes everything in its path - a danger to all!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wanted:</strong> A random player is marked. If they survive, they win. If they die, their killer wins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more surprises 🐔</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Cactus-Steam_Plan_de_travail_1_copie_2.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330290/extras/Montage-Banière-Argent-V8-Trans.png?t=1769532438\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gold Coins - </strong>Collect gold coins (the game's currency) to customize your cactus. The more you earn, the more cosmetics you unlock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Our Complete Vision (In Development)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CactusBandido doesn't stop at Gold Rush! We have planned:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎮 Phase 1 - Demo (Q1 2026)</strong><br>Test Gold Rush for free with the community. Your feedback directly shapes the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🚀 Phase 2 - Early Access</strong><br>Team variants (2v2v2 and 3v3), more modes, more worlds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏆 Phase 3 - Gold Release</strong><br>Varied secondary modes (PvE, co-op, fun mini-games), more maps, full content.</p></li></ul>",
